ss=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 30, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zty1665703129216.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zty1665703129216.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zty1665703129216.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zty1665703129216\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Declarations Container\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Code container for defining constants with object scope.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zty1665703129216__section_w396ab1b5b3_w397ab1b5_w398ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d624269e51\">\n                     \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zty1665703129216__p_d115844e1_d115845e1_d115846e1\">A constant that is declared in the Declarations code container of a component, entity, or field is available for the entire object and its child objects.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"zty1665703129216__note_w399ab1b5b3b5_w400ab1b5b3_w401ab1b5_w402ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Constants defined in the Declarations container of a component entity are accessible to its fields, but not to its inner entities.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zty1665703129216__section_m33_xc3_fcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d624269e63\">\n                        Defining and Referencing Compile-Time Constants</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zty1665703129216__d6767e82\">To declare a compile-time constant, use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#define</span> pre-compiler directive. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#define APP_VERSION = \"2.1.00\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zty1665703129216__d6767e92\">To reference the constant in ProcScript, enclose the\n\t\tname within angle brackets as\n\t\t<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ConstantName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;</code>. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">putmess &lt;APP_VERSION&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zty1665703129216__d6767e109\">During compilation, Uniface replaces the constant\n\t\tname with the actual value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zty1665703129216__d6767e112\">It is also possible to remove a constant using the\n\t\t<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#undefine</span> directive. \n                           <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ots1665702620497.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ots1665702620497.html\" title=\"Define a constant name and value.\">#define</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ktw1665702620584.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ktw1665702620584.html\" title=\"Undefine a constant for the scope of the constant declaration.\">#undefine</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zty1665703129216__section_dxh_bf3_fcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d624269e119\">Example: Defining Constants</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zty1665703129216__pre_m1x_wf3_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#define frmEntity = firstOuterMostEntity</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zty1665703129216__pre_n1x_wf3_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#comment Session Service for processing a request\n#define mySessionService =</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zty1665703129216__pre_o1x_wf3_fcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#comment DTD for defining the format of the XML data to be interchanged with the Session Service.\n#comment The DTD must be defined as dtdName.modelName, uppercased and fully qualified\n#comment for example:\n\n#define myDtd = CUSTOMERDTD.MYMODEL</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qzg1665702620270.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Constants</a><p>A constant is a value that remains unchanged during the course of code execution.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534614\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534614\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Declarations Container Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 30, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Declarations Container Code container for defining constants with object scope. Description A constant that is declared in the Declarations code container of a component, entity, or field is available for the entire object and its child objects. Note: Constants defined in the Declarations container of a component entity are accessible to its fields, but not to its inner entities. Defining and Referencing Compile-Time Constants To declare a compile-time constant, use the #define pre-compiler directive. For example: #define APP_VERSION = \"2.1.00\" Copy To reference the constant in ProcScript, enclose the name within angle brackets as < ConstantName > . For example: putmess <APP_VERSION> Copy During compilation, Uniface replaces the constant name with the actual value. It is also possible to remove a constant using the #undefine directive. #define and #undefine Example: Defining Constants #define frmEntity = firstOuterMostEntity Copy #comment Session Service for processing a request #define mySessionService = Copy #comment DTD for defining the format of the XML data to be interchanged with the Session Service. #comment The DTD must be defined as dtdName.modelName, uppercased and fully qualified #comment for example: #define myDtd = CUSTOMERDTD.MYMODEL Copy Related Links Constants A constant is a value that remains unchanged during the course of code execution. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}